Ohrid.country: Macedonia, the Former Yugoslav Republic of

reviews.text: The owners are very helpful and nice. We got what we expected - the price was really good as well as the location. Our room even had a huge balcony overlooking the sea! We've spent a pleasant and relaxing night here. Unfortunately the owners don't speak English.
Basic hotel, good if you need to spend A night!
Old fashioned, be a tourists as they were 40 years ago. The place is beautifull un a Wes Anderson sense, but a dirty common bath kind of ruins the experience.
